wings, nails and beak 1. 28. 19, 20, 22.
[According to Nī., name of a Yakṣa, cf.
अश्वक्रन्दादयो नव यक्षाः on 1. 32. 18
Bom. Ed.].

प्रवेपन
Pravepana m.: A mythical serpent.
Born in the कुल of Takṣaka, listed by
Sūta among those offered in the snake sacri-
fice of Janamejaya 1. 52. 8, 7, 9.

प्रहस
Prahasa m.: A mythical serpent,
Born in the कुल of Dhṛtarāṣṭra, listed
