Son of Surasā and Kaśyapa 5. 101. 4,
17; description 5. 101. 5-7; also listed by
Sūta among the sons of Kadrū 1. 31. 14, 2.

मुण्ड
Muṇḍa m.: A mythical serpent.
Born in the कुल of Kauravya, listed by
