श्रीवह
Śrīvaha m.: A mythical serpent.
Son of Kadrū, listed among her sons
by Sūta at the request of Śaunaka
1. 31. 13, 2.

श्रुतसेन
Śrutasena m.: A mythical serpent.
Referred to by Uttaṅka in his praise of
