(अनुगम्यमाना … भरतस्त्रीभिर्) went to
Bhāgīrathī 13. 154. 16; (55) Arjuna and
Kṛṣṇa saw Subhadrā and all other Bharata
women surrounding Gāndhārī (सर्वा
