स्वबाहुबलम् आश्रितः॥) 8. 5. 15; (46)
After the fall of Duryodhana, when Bala-
rāma, in anger, left for Dvārakā, Pāñcālas
and Vārṣṇeyas were disheartened (पाञ्चालाश्
